parts.markscheme:
- Quadratic formula:  
  \(\displaystyle\sin x=\frac{1\pm\sqrt{1-4(6)(-2)}}{12}
  =\frac{1\pm\sqrt{1+48}}{12}
  =\frac{1\pm7}{12}.\) <marks>M1</marks>  
- Thus \(\sin x=\dfrac{2}{3}\) or \(\sin x=-\dfrac{1}{2}.\) <marks>A1</marks>
